#. module: it_hardware
#: model:product.template,description_sale:it_hardware.product_template_7
msgid ""
"A 35.5cms (14) 2-in-1 touchscreen laptop, the ThinkPad X1 Yoga Gen 7 delivers features that matter.\n"
"        Enjoy the spectacular Communications Bar that raises the bar on collaboration.\n"
"        Robust security includes Tile® tracking technology—just in case.\n"
"        Plus, high-performance 12th Gen Intel® Core™ vPro processing, on the Intel® Evo™ platform provides super-responsive, on-the-go power."
msgstr ""
"ແລັບທັອບໜ້າຈໍສຳຜັດແບບ 2-in-1 ຂະໜາດ 35.5cms (14), ThinkPad X1 Yoga Gen 7 ມາພ້ອມຄຸນສົມບັ"
"ດທີ່ສຳຄັນ.\n"
"        ເພີດເພີນກັບ Communications Bar ທີ່ຊ່ວຍຍົກລະດັບການເຮັດວຽກຮ່ວມກັນ.\n"
"        ລະບົບຄວາມປອດໄພທີ່ແຂງແກ່ນ ລວມທັງເຕັກໂນໂລຊີການຕິດຕາມ Tile®.\n"
"        ພ້ອມທັງປະສິດທິພາບສູງຈາກໜ່ວຍປະມວນຜົນ 12th Gen Intel® Core™ vPro ເທິງແພລັດຟອມ "
"Intel® Evo™ ທີ່ໃຫ້ພະລັງງານຕອບສະໜອງໄດ້ດີເລີດທຸກບ່ອນ."

