#. module: it_hardware
#: model:product.template,description_sale:it_hardware.product_template_4
msgid ""
"Our lightest ever ThinkPad, the ThinkPad X1 Nano Gen 2 weighs from just 970g / 2.14lbs but packs a punch.\n"
"        With up to 12th Gen Intel® Core™ vPro® processors, it has optional 5G connectivity and comes with advanced biometric and AI-based security, plus smart battery-saving features.\n"
"        Just as impressive is the truly stunning viewing and immersive audio experience it gives you."
msgstr ""
"ThinkPad ທີ່ເບົາທີ່ສຸດເທົ່າທີ່ເຄີຍມີມາ, ThinkPad X1 Nano Gen 2 ມີນ້ຳໜັກພຽງ 970g ແຕ່ເຕັມໄປດ້ວຍປະ"
"ສິດທິພາບ.\n"
"        ດ້ວຍໜ່ວຍປະມວນຜົນສູງສຸດ 12th Gen Intel® Core™ vPro®, ຮອງຮັບ 5G ແລະ ມາພ້ອມລະບົບ"
"ຄວາມປອດໄພແບບໄບໂອເມຕຣິກ ແລະ AI, ພ້ອມທັງຄຸນສົມບັດປະຢັດແບັດເຕີຣີອັດສະລິຍະ.\n"
"        ສ້າງຄວາມປະທັບໃຈດ້ວຍປະສົບການການເບິ່ງທີ່ສວຍງາມ ແລະ ລະບົບສຽງທີ່ສົມຈິງ."

#. module: it_hardware
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:it_hardware.homepage
msgid ""
"Our mission is to give customers the best experience.<br/>\n"
"                                            Extensive documentation &amp;amp; guides, an active community,<br/>\n"
"                                            24/7 support make it a pleasure to work with us."
